reviewText: Great information -- used it in preparation for an upcoming visit to London.
I enjoyed this a lot, since I am not able to fly. This one focused on specific areas of London, it was a bit different in that aspect.
As a general tour it was satisfying. Not a lot of detail, but very comprehensive. A near video.

Whoever did these series on world cities has destroyed all or any visual value with the most god awful "music" hammering away in the background. Lonon is no different than Salzburg.  How could this occur? Stupid, dumb, awful -- and we quit.
A little dated maybe,but overall a great overview of London.
This video enumerates places to go in London. A good reference for anyone planning to go there.
